 research reward tiles</li><li>24 temple tiles</li><li>5 blocking tiles</li><li>15 rival action tiles</li><li>27 cardboard coin tokens</li><li>27 cardboard compass tokens</li><li>16 plastic tablet tokens</li><li>12 plastic arrowhead tokens</li><li>9 plastic jewel tokens</li><li>10 fear tiles</li><li>1 starting player marker</li><li>1 cardboard moon staff</li><li>4 quick reference sheets</li><li>1 rulebook</li></ul></div></div><div class="article__section"><picture class="picture overflow-hidden radius radius--semi"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8869/67e5412b9fea6c4b27e1b0fc_Components%20Photo.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Lost Ruins of Arnak" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8869/67e5412b9fea6c4b27e1b0fc_Components%20Photo-p-500.webp 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8869/67e5412b9fea6c4b27e1b0fc_Components%20Photo-p-800.webp 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8869/67e5412b9fea6c4b27e1b0fc_Components%20Photo-p-1080.webp 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8869/67e5412b9fea6c4b27e1b0fc_Components%20Photo.webp 1500w"/></picture></div><div id="videos-hr" class="hr w-embed"><hr style="margin: 0 auto; border: 0.0625rem solid #F2F2F2;" /></div><div id="videos" class="article__section"><h2 style="color:hsla(145.99999999999997, 46.88%, 25.10%, 1.00)" class="h2 title title--upper margin--bottom-3 margin--bottom-4-lg">Videos</h2><div class="swiper js-swiper-videos margin--bottom-3 margin--bottom-4-lg w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="swiper-wrapper w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="swiper-slide w-dyn-item"><div class="w-embed w-iframe"><iframe class="video video--youtube radius radius--semi" width="100%" height="200" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-VewiWsLJmQ?si=cJS2MpQGmbpMuwT7" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-p