</svg>
</button></div><div class="w-layout-grid grid grid--flex grid--bottom"><div class="cell cell--12 cell--shrink-lg hide-tablet"><picture class="picture picture--complaint"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8857/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8afc_cge_complaint%402x.webp" loading="lazy" width="496" sizes="(max-width: 991px) 100vw, 496px" alt="" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8857/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8afc_cge_complaint%25402x-p-500.webp 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8857/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8afc_cge_complaint%25402x-p-800.webp 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8857/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8afc_cge_complaint%402x.webp 992w"/></picture></div><div class="cell cell--12 cell--auto-lg"><div class="modal__content modal__content--complaint"><h2 class="h2 title title--upper color--white margin--bottom-1">How to make <span class="color--secondary-yellow-300">a complaint?</span></h2><h3 class="h4 title color--white margin--bottom-3 margin--bottom-55-lg">B2B only</h3><p class="text text--18 color--white margin--bottom-3 margin--bottom-55-lg">Terms and conditions for resolving any new complaints of damaged games during transport: <a href="mailto:iva@czechgames.com" class="link color--white text-weight-bold">iva@czechgames.com</a></p><div class="w-layout-grid grid grid--flex grid--gap-h grid--gap-v"><div class="cell cell--12 cell--6-md"><div class="text text--18 text-weight-bold color--secondary-yellow-300 text--thin margin--bottom-2">Reach us and provide following documents and pictures:</div><ul role="list" class="list list--bullet list--inverse"><li class="text text--18 color--white">We need a scan of a document stating that the shipment arrived damaged.</li><li class="text text--18 color--white">Provide a picture of a whole pallet with the damage.</li><li class="text text--18 color--white">Provide a picture of the damaged games (ex. 3 damaged Codenames = one picture with 3 Codenames where the damage is obvious).</li></ul></div><div class="cell cell--12 cell--6-md"><div class="text text--18 text-weight-bold color--secondary-yellow-300 text--thin margin--bottom-2">We will evaluate the damage and issue a credit note for you:</div><ul role="list" class="list list--bullet list--inverse"><li class="text text--18 color--white">We do not accept complaints when only the game foil is damaged a bit.</li><li class="text text--18 color--white">If there is only a box damaged and the game itself is still ok, you receive 50% discount.</li><li class="text text--18 color--white">If the game is damaged a lot, you receive 80% discount.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></footer></div><script src="https://d3e54v103j8qbb.cloudfront.net/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.dc5e7f18c8.js?site=67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8857" type="text/javascript" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><script src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8857/js/webflow.schunk.36b8fb49256177c8.js" type="text/javascript" integrity="sha384-4abIlA5/v7XaW1HMXKBgnUuhnjBYJ/Z9C1OSg4OhmVw9O3QeHJ/qJqFBERCDPv7G" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><script src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8857/js/webflow.schunk.2334eca497fab7e3.js" type="text/javascript" integrity="sha384-2ygWeOdgo20pazDhKeURD3S9it5yXw8Dl25D4BL67equ+I3InX7aDRvuOieZoiN6" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><script src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67d17a45b4e1484b40ea8857/js/webflow.12d81a53.cd169bd720fa3a8b.js" type="text/javascript" integrity="sha384-4eErVy3nJ0IfiruxdSeme7evdatO97xnrU3e/cXfzRblQ+R2IPw/v/yDAKkIWW53" crossorigin="anonymous"></script><!--<script>
let lastScrollTop = 0;
const navbar = document.querySelector('.js-sticky-header');

window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    let scrollTop = window.scrollY;
    
    if (scrollTop > lastScrollTop) {
        // Scroll dolů - skryj navigaci
        navbar.style.transform = 'translateY(-100%)';
    } else {
        // Scroll nahoru - zobraz navigaci
        navbar.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
    }
    
    lastScrollTop = scrollTop;
});

</script>--></body></html>